Patient Check-In
    ↓
Front Desk Registration
    - Manual data entry of demographics & insurance
    - Paper-based consent forms
    ↓
Nurse / MA Triage
    - Manually enter vitals and chief complaint
    - Redundant data fields across modules
    ↓
Provider Encounter
    - Manual note-taking during encounter
    - Limited EHR templates or smart phrases
    ↓
Documentation & Order Entry
    - Separate order entry screen (not integrated)
    - Manual problem list and diagnosis updates
    ↓
Billing & Coding Review
    - Manual coding review post-visit
    - Frequent rework due to incomplete documentation
    ↓
Discharge & Follow-Up
    - Printed discharge summary
    - Follow-up scheduling requires separate system
